* Iron Raptor looked down at the tiny kitten in her arms, seeing that he was 
peaceful and content.< Lucky little bugger!> so her thoughts said.
He was so small and innocent, not really knowing of any of the dangers which 
he had been around, but tucked safely in her back compartment.
She smiled down at the little guy, wiggling her fingers and tickling his 
side for a second. But then her back bolted straight and she starred 
bug-eyed for a second before looking down at her leg.
Snow Tech was attached to it and bawling his eyes out!
Iron Raptor expression turned to that of annoyance, rolling her eyes and 
then looking over at Shadow Cat.
Her suggestion was very acceptable at this point.
She looked down at Snow Tech with the same expression, a flat voice which 
she was sure he knew well.*

" Let go...of my leg."

* Just then she recieved the transmission from Hysteria, replying.*

" Just take your time, we can wait a few cycles."
